Member Enumeration Documentation

enum iproc::IValueSupplier::ValueTypeId

Define standard value types.

Enumerator:
VTI_AUTO  Automatic value, implementation specific.
VTI_POSITION  Value of position (2D or 3D).
VTI_RADIUS  Value of radius.
VTI_QUALITY  Quality factor.

This value should be normalized to range [0, 1].

VTI_ANGLE  Angle in radian.
VTI_LENGTH  Length or distance.
